\v 4 \add Z\add*ehlukaniseleni impi limelene layo;\x + 12.3; 22.27; 51.27,28. Jow. 3.9.\x* sukumani, kasenyuke emini enkulu.\x + 15.8.\x* Maye kithi! ngoba ilanga selithambeme\f + \fk selithambeme: \fl Heb. \fq seliphendukile.\f*\x + Hlab. 90.9.\x*, ngoba amathunzi okuhlwa aselulekile.
\v 5 Sukumani, senyuke ngobusuku, sidilize izigodlo zayo.
